lu_part1: Wou kee Mann ass, ass kee Rot,
lu_part2: wou keng Fra ass, ass kee Stot.
en_literal_translation_p1: Where there is no man, there is no advice,
en_literal_translation_p2: where there is no woman, there is no home.
en_closest_real_corresponding_saying_p1: A house without a man is like a ship without a captain,
en_closest_real_corresponding_saying_p2: but a home without a woman is like a body without a soul.
